      <p class="max-w-[950px] mx-auto text-[17.5px] leading-8"> Well-drafted contracts are the foundation of secure business relationships. Professional agreement drafting ensures clarity, enforceability, risk mitigation, and legal protection in commercial transactions. </p> </section><section class="px-5 py-[60px] bg-white">
